    com.liferay.portal.model.ModelListener<AHOffer>

    public class AHOfferListener
extends AbstactInnerModelListener<AHOffer>
    The listener interface for receiving AHOffer events. The class that is interested in processing a AHOffer event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addAHOfferListener method. When the AHOffer event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
